      <h1>The search history</h1>
      <?CHUNK filename="help/contact-us.chnk" optional="1"?>
      <p> The search history keeps a record of the searches you have submitted during your current
                     session. The history keeps track of your query terms, the collections that were searched, and a
                     summary of your results. The query terms are displayed as links that, if clicked, will resubmit
                     the search. (Fig. 1)
